<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Denzel Marani - Photography Portfolio</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 50px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.3em;
            color: #764ba2;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        .divider {
            width: 100px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #667eea;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        .intro-section {
            margin: 40px 0;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .intro-section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .intro-section p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .highlight {
            color: #764ba2;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .gallery-preview {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .gallery-item {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            aspect-ratio: 1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #667eea;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 10px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: #764ba2;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #eee;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }

        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 30px;
            }

            h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }

            .intro-section h2 {
                font-size: 1.4em;
            }

            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 15px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>Denzel Marani</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Photography & Visual Arts</p>
            <div class="divider"></div>
        </header>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>Welcome</h2>
            <p>
                Hi! I'm <span class="highlight">Denzel Marani</span>, a passionate photographer dedicated to capturing moments that tell stories. 
                With a keen eye for detail and a love for visual storytelling, I specialize in creating compelling imagery across various genres.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>About My Work</h2>
            <p>
                My portfolio showcases a diverse range of photography projects. From stunning landscapes to intimate portraits, 
                each image is crafted with intention and care. I believe in the power of photography to <span class="highlight">inspire, 
                connect, and preserve</span> meaningful moments.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>Portfolio Categories</h2>
            <div class="gallery-preview">
                <div class="gallery-item">Portraits</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Landscapes</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Events</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Lifestyle</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Travel</div>
                <div class="gallery-item">Nature</div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="intro-section">
            <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
            <p>
                Interested in commissioning a photo session or learning more about my work? 
                I'd love to hear from you!
            </p>
            <button class="cta-button">View Full Portfolio</button>
            <button class="cta-button">Get in Touch</button>
        </section>

        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Denzel Marani Photography. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
    